//program-think.blogspot.com/2013/06/weekly-share-53.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6944453719343094575","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/6944453719343094575","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2013年6月3日 12:36:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"DU8NQHw4eip7ImA9XBBTE0w.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4695646623282465005"},"published":{"$t":"2019-06-12T13:38:11.232+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-06-12T13:38:11.232+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2019-06-12T13:38:11.232+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 12楼的网友\n天朝的未来，确实不太乐观。\n内部外部，都有很多难搞的问题。\n这方面的讨论，俺在博..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 12楼的网友<br />天朝的未来，确实不太乐观。<br />内部外部，都有很多难搞的问题。<br />这方面的讨论，俺在博文和评论区中，都多次提及了。<br />（可以使用界面右侧栏的【站内搜索】功能，找到相关讨论）<br /><br />虽然形势不乐观，<br />但未来始终是不确定的，每个人都可以尽自己的微薄之力，作出一些影响。<br />以本人为例：当初刚开博客的时候，完全没有想到这个博客能影响这么多人。<br /><br />俺的希望是：<br />未来的转型是尽可能是低成本的，并且能逐步转型为成熟的民主体制。<br />俺能做到是：<br />尽量普及【政治素质】和【心理素质】。这两点，对未来的转型期会有帮助"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/511921656416563357/comments/default/4695646623282465005?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/511921656416563357/comments/default/4695646623282465005?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/06/weekly-share-131.html?showComment=1560317891232#c4695646623282465005","title":"每周转载&#65306;&#8220;六四事件&#8221;30周年纪念&#65288;各方外媒报道&#65292;多图&#65289;"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/511921656416563357/comments/default/1316561298832713792?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"nore